      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>ğŸ¦¸â€â™€ï¸ My IEP Hero</h1>
      <div class="subtitle">Your IEP Advocacy Platform is Live!</div>
      
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">ğŸ“š <strong>Parent Basic Plan</strong> - $19/month</div>
        <div class="feature">â­ <strong>Parent Premium Plan</strong> - $39/month</div>
        <div class="feature">ğŸ† <strong>Parent Pro Plan</strong> - $59/month</div>
        <div class="feature">ğŸ’¼ <strong>Professional Advocate Plans</strong> - $75-199/month</div>
